      "title": "Token from tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Minister Kanchana Wijesekera said the token system for distribution of fuel at petrol stations would be introduced from tomorrow (27), adding that the date of arrival of the next fuel tanker could not be stated at present."
